<section xml:id="C6.S15">
<title>Sums</title>        
  
 
<para xml:id="C6.S15.p1">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="1" xml:id="C6.S15.p1.s1">
 <Math equation-number="6.15.1" mode="display" xml:id="C6.S15.E1">\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\mathrm{Ci}\left(\pi n\right)=\tfrac{1}{2}(\ln 2-\gamma),</Math> , <Math equation-number="6.15.2" mode="display" xml:id="C6.S15.E2">\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\frac{\mathrm{si}\left(\pi n\right)}{n}=\tfrac{1}{2}\pi(\ln \pi-1),</Math> <Math equation-number="6.15.3" mode="display" xml:id="C6.S15.E3">\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}(-1)^{n}\mathrm{Ci}\left(2\pi n\right)=1-\ln 2-\tfrac{1}{2}\gamma,</Math> , <Math equation-number="6.15.4" mode="display" xml:id="C6.S15.E4">\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}(-1)^{n}\frac{\mathrm{si}\left(2\pi n\right)}{n}=\pi(\tfrac {3}{2}\ln 2-1)</Math>.
</sentence>

</para>
 
<para xml:id="C6.S15.p2">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="2" xml:id="C6.S15.p2.s1">
For further sums see Fempl (1960),Hansen (1975, pp. 423–424), Harris (2000),Prudnikov et al. (1986b, vol. 2, pp. 649–650), and Slavić (1974).
</sentence>

</para>

 
